{"tid":2101141,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【港版國安法】太古城賣盤飆至近500個 移民佔5% 學者：下半年樓價仍睇升","createTime":"2020-07-09T14:42:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-09T14:53:54.000Z","uid":88743,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"506542df7196f05055108b290328baa46ab3b005","tid":2101141,"uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T14:42:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20200709/GR6NCC75KEDYJ5PXEPWLSJCAUY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200709%2FGR6NCC75KEDYJ5PXEPWLSJCAUY%2F&d=gCjj53haX7oQ0UVj6qLsjnqjnVJZrvj6qhhAu%2BA3ahw%3D&h=433bacf5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200709%2FGR6NCC75KEDYJ5PXEPWLSJCAUY%2F&h=5a3fc9f2\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20200709/GR6NCC75KEDYJ5PXEPWLSJCAUY/</a><br />\n港版國安法實施後，引起港人不安，新一波疫情下樓市恐再釀移民賣樓潮。屬中產屋苑之一的鰂魚涌太古城，本月放盤量突飆升至近500個，按月升一成，屬近年新高。而據中原地產網上搵樓平台，全港二手租售放盤量共28,618個，與上月同期28,058個比較，略增560個或2%。不過，二手放盤量增加，樓價未必即時受壓，有學者估計下半年樓價仍會上升5%。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0aMLV3L.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0aMLV3L.jpg&h=8217133b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cb8025db25d0a75598beedf77416171eb1547abd","tid":2101141,"uid":287422,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T14:43:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a428e529193cc2cd4db7331c8a2f88b47bf1d82","tid":2101141,"uid":343361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T14:45:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"29f309fa60a3aaa452e663452e6fecead24f4791","tid":2101141,"uid":43751,"like